{"tid":2082071,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【試着說】党安法 【正視聽】党安法","createTime":"2020-06-27T17:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T14:22:54.000Z","uid":301327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7c8365609ef118854eb4c7b0643e05bfb8ac5902","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"支共分明係擺港人資產上枱同侵侵 曬冷，諗住先發制侵展過第二階段貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n他使用的是<strong>「邊際策略」（brinkmanship）</strong>：通過認為製造不存在的危機，不惜把雙方拉至戰爭邊緣，卻在危機不可收拾前退讓，以謀求最大利益。<br />\n那是始創於美國總統艾森豪時期的國務卿杜勒斯（John Foster Dulles），將衝突情况逐步升級，直至戰爭爆發邊緣，藉此施加強大壓力，迫使對方作出對己有利的退讓。<br />\n<br />\n【壹週平行時空】Brinkmanship vs. brinkmanship（沈旭暉）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_736980_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_736980_0&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=2362a627\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_736980_0&h=8297f115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_736980_0</a>"},{"pid":"94ae2c2454f801a4237ac6f5e49185e1415b2f99","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"要回應brinkmanship，自然要知己知彼：<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 香港不是新疆、西藏，畢竟資訊透明，香港人必須向國際社會說明，香港的抗爭並非恐怖主義：定義上這屬於學術問題、另文再敘；方法論上可多與各地同期發生的抗爭比較（同期差不多有20國發生類似大型抗爭，無一被列為恐怖主義）；行動上必須保留大量證據，證明香港警察的暴力才是不成比例的暴力；文宣上要證明「全國性法律等於香港endgame」，因為足以影響各國在香港的戰略利益。這是國際線最重要的工作。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 要回應溫水煮蛙策略，但又要市民保持希望，議會路線的朋友，應該有兩手準備，當DQ局限於案例，未改變權力結構，則要安排大量Plan B；當DQ針對整個陣營（例如「反對23條就不能選議員」），則必須及早製造文宣，向全港市民、全球受眾講解，這也是等於香港endgame，並以現任議員維繫一個國際認受的民選mandate（授權），保留元氣。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 當上述情況出現，移民潮也肯定隨之而來，屆時重點是希望離開的香港人不要獨善其身，在海外也可以維繫香港人身份認同，繼續用不同方式凝聚起來。「移民成為廢老」和「走到海外成為diaspora心繫香港」，差之毫釐，謬之千里。但經過過去一年的洗禮，要放棄一切，談何容易？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ztXFWb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ztXFWb.gif&h=99183429&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c948e5c67c3ee7ff638284091f8457e752fbd4c","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:22:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b31e5cd17d4f918d30b79e7b85b0c6bee774208b","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:23:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"86db8dfa83eb8d58ba552e18d182a30b729e8509","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:25:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7077b0ce5d8ae0afc357749a30bd2d67f00438da","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"賭一國兩制 還党安管治"},{"pid":"877f325c0e500893a8ed3b99b634411a91891818","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:30:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d83674b8a7dea63bd5899681ea080160bd40766","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:32:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db3a72bab18bf2dba8219ec02809c8dba5d46380","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:37:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"591763ba874244c27e2649f93a5c746fd5b1bd5d","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:43:57.000Z","msg":"【突發時空．沈旭暉 004】國安法：中國的現實主義框架，會否誤判？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HjhRbV8qTgo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHjhRbV8qTgo&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=aaf18a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HjhRbV8qTgo</a>"},{"pid":"146d780e55a6fd876baf9dc4bab67f66e9c220ab","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:45:47.000Z","msg":"賭一國兩制 還党安管治"},{"pid":"cb7eae9e1626d739a24196a91745e26ea0d6d445","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:53:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b3df76ab758ca4fc3c4259d018b182a708f81240","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T17:59:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b4dd1c9d047c04a4a1336ece7c983c3eefb051b","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T18:03:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c3ef3d6454d4cb922d9ca3527b21b8d3d5f71913","tid":2082071,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:22:54.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}